{"tid":729922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港逾70萬公屋戶 9月加租10%","createTime":"2018-07-05T03:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T04:55:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3a3249472e6a5ba55261e90bbf2f35ff4a1a38","tid":729922,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"公屋租金每兩年調整一次，今年全港逾70萬公屋居民又要加租。根據政府數字，過去兩年間，公屋租戶平均家庭收入的增幅較租金上調幅度為高，上升幅度為11.59%，因此按機制於今年9月上調公屋租金一成。此次是自2008年有公屋檢討機制後第5次加租。<br />\n<br />\n根據房委會於2018年1月通過的預算，2018-19年度租住房屋運作帳目的赤字預計約為11億元。在公屋租金於2018年9月上調10%後，2018-19年度的赤字預計會減至0.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180705/58402207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402207&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=660b41d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402207&h=4f646fe5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180705/58402207</a>"},{"pid":"e938e8db0ddc97ceb8ec1dca95f69551e38560f1","tid":729922,"uid":181439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"So?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加完咪又係月租唔夠1500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181bbc57e3c1051ee4add2472ded3779ab0ca3ac","tid":729922,"uid":44958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e938e8db0ddc97ceb8ec1dca95f69551e38560f1","tid":729922,"uid":181439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"So?<img sr